\end_layout

\end_inset

Sean 
\begin_inset Formula $f:A\to B$
\end_inset

 un homomorfismo, 
\begin_inset Formula $a\in A$
\end_inset

 y 
\begin_inset Formula $x,y\in\ker f$
\end_inset

.
